<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Project:CAMAY! üåü</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .confirmation-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #D8C1A9;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .confirmation-button:hover {
      background-color: #E8D9C2;
      color: white;
    }
    .signature {
      color: #555;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>üåü Welcome to Project:CAMAY! üåü</h1>
    <p>We are thrilled to have you join Project:CAMAY, a vibrant community celebrating the artistry and craftsmanship of Filipino artisans and the passion of art enthusiasts like yourself.</p>
    <p>To embark on this creative journey, please confirm your account by clicking the link below:</p>
    <a href="<%= url_for(controller: 'users', action: 'confirm_email', token: @user.confirmation_token, only_path: false) %>" class="confirmation-button">Confirm Your Email</a>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to us via this email address. We are dedicated to ensuring you have an exceptional experience. ü§ù</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing to be a part of Project:CAMAY. We can't wait to witness the incredible contributions you'll make to our community! üé®</p>
    <p class="signature">Warm regards,<br>The Project:CAMAY Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
